plot: Aaron and Rachel speculate on the extreme effects of Nano technology. Meanwhile a figure from Miles's past reemerges.

Texas Rangers arrive in Willoughby wanting to know just what the Patriots are doing on their sovereign territory. Miles is behind it having written to them about the situation. It turns out however that Miles once tried to kill the head Ranger, John Fry. Miles takes a patriot soldier prisoner hoping to get information to convince Fry the Patriots are also his enemy. Monroe has a different approach to starting a war between Texas and the new US government. Aaron is having difficulty coming to grips with the new power he seems to now have.—garykmcd
